                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000029a09a-be5b-4dc8-b663-04299b1f9465" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(x\right)=x+\frac{1}{x},\ x&gt;0⇒{f}^{{'}}\left(x\right)=1-\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}=0\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000029a09a-be5b-4dc8-b663-04299b1f9465 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000aef7dc27-a41f-460f-9266-8a6256f15efc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{1}{{x}^{2}}=1⇒{x}^{2}=1⇒x=1\ (x&gt;0)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001aef7dc27-a41f-460f-9266-8a6256f15efc"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000aef7dc27-a41f-460f-9266-8a6256f15efc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001aef7dc27-a41f-460f-9266-8a6256f15efc {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8"> </span><span class="pt-0000020aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8">Pig we›`</span><span class="pt-0000020aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8">y‡Z</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(f\left(x\right)=1+\frac{1}{1}=2\ \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010aa36171-003e-45a3-9159-b7b80b28e2c8