                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000057fbc7ec-7e9a-49f2-b3ab-6e17beec402a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(h=\frac{1}{2}\ g{t}^{2}=\frac{1}{2}\times 10\times {4}^{2}=80m\ ;\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000157fbc7ec-7e9a-49f2-b3ab-6e17beec402a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000057fbc7ec-7e9a-49f2-b3ab-6e17beec402a {line-height: 115.0%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000157fbc7ec-7e9a-49f2-b3ab-6e17beec402a {font-family: Arial;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000faa5be7d-ba03-4c21-9921-2c2e4923d63b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(h=v{t}^{{'}}⇒v=\frac{80}{4.25-4}=320\ m{s}^{-1}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001faa5be7d-ba03-4c21-9921-2c2e4923d63b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000faa5be7d-ba03-4c21-9921-2c2e4923d63b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001faa5be7d-ba03-4c21-9921-2c2e4923d63b {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
