                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000ec9c4e4-33c8-4644-81e9-d091fa6924e1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∵\displaystyle\int_{0}^{2} f\left(x\right)dx=2∴\displaystyle\int_{0}^{2} f\left(z\right)dz=2……(i)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010ec9c4e4-33c8-4644-81e9-d091fa6924e1"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000ec9c4e4-33c8-4644-81e9-d091fa6924e1 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010ec9c4e4-33c8-4644-81e9-d091fa6924e1 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008c99164f-4cae-4b04-8c4b-d85ea41f579a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000018c99164f-4cae-4b04-8c4b-d85ea41f579a">GLb</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018c99164f-4cae-4b04-8c4b-d85ea41f579a">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\displaystyle\int_{-\frac{1}{2}}^{\frac{1}{2}} f\left(1-2x\right)dx\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008c99164f-4cae-4b04-8c4b-d85ea41f579a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018c99164f-4cae-4b04-8c4b-d85ea41f579a {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a2798ebe-6535-4390-a899-d7c2ce7e7091" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=-\frac{1}{2}\displaystyle\int_{2}^{0} f\left(z\right)dz=\frac{1}{2}\displaystyle\int_{0}^{2} f\left(z\right)dz=\frac{1}{2}\times 2=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a2798ebe-6535-4390-a899-d7c2ce7e7091"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a2798ebe-6535-4390-a899-d7c2ce7e7091 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a2798ebe-6535-4390-a899-d7c2ce7e7091 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91">awi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(1-2x=z\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒-2dx=dz\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴dx=-\frac{1}{2}dz\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a8827f2a-4b4a-469f-8770-78d772558f91 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b5509865-07ff-4c54-b915-156996be8743" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b5509865-07ff-4c54-b915-156996be8743"><img src="#" style="width: 1.014741in;height: 0.6722649in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b5509865-07ff-4c54-b915-156996be8743 {}span.pt-000001b5509865-07ff-4c54-b915-156996be8743 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
