                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000012931cb4-c859-45fd-8756-21dbe30fc47e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000112931cb4-c859-45fd-8756-21dbe30fc47e"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int_{0}^{2} \left| x\right| dx=\int_{0}^{2} xdx\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000012931cb4-c859-45fd-8756-21dbe30fc47e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000112931cb4-c859-45fd-8756-21dbe30fc47e {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006cd591e4-6fda-49b8-a1cd-2d731a39060e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{1}{2}\ {\left[ {x}^{2}\right] }_{0}^{2}=\frac{1}{2}\left[ {\left(2\right)}^{2}-{0}^{2}\right] =\frac{1}{2}\times 4=2\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016cd591e4-6fda-49b8-a1cd-2d731a39060e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006cd591e4-6fda-49b8-a1cd-2d731a39060e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016cd591e4-6fda-49b8-a1cd-2d731a39060e {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
