                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000099d75f97-7cae-43e4-be4d-957b038f5eaf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000199d75f97-7cae-43e4-be4d-957b038f5eaf"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 1.083333in;height: 0.5578839in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000099d75f97-7cae-43e4-be4d-957b038f5eaf {}span.pt-00000199d75f97-7cae-43e4-be4d-957b038f5eaf {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cf0841c1-768d-4d8f-b1f7-56def51be538" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{P}{BC}=\frac{3P}{AC}=\frac{4P}{AB}….(i)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cf0841c1-768d-4d8f-b1f7-56def51be538"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cf0841c1-768d-4d8f-b1f7-56def51be538 {}span.pt-000001cf0841c1-768d-4d8f-b1f7-56def51be538 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000081d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000181d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6">Avevi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000181d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{P}{AD}=\frac{3P}{BD}=\frac{4P}{AB}….\ (ii)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000181d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000081d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000181d9cea5-dd63-4ba2-81ce-3fb36b349ec6 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000dd66f3c0-44f5-4e64-9e89-ea1d459951bf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" s